### ðŸ§ª Sample Rules

|| CSS Selector || Message ||
\| `button:not([aria-label])` | Missing ARIA label |
\| `.btn.red` | Unauthorized color |
\| `h1 + h3` | Skipped heading level |
\| `div[style*="font-size:"]` | Inline font-size used |

